# Project TODO — C Problem Solving Framework

## 🧱 Core Architecture
- [x] Finalize clean separation:
  - `driver.c` (framework)
  - `problem.c` (input + output print)
  - `solver.c` (algorithm only)
  - `judge.c` (expected output + compare)
- [x] Standardize headers (`problem.h`, `solver.h`, `judge.h`, `problem_types.h`)
- [x] Create a reusable folder template for new problems

